PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT CONTENTSTATUSHISTORYID, CONTENTID, REVISIONID, LASTMODIFIERNAME, STATENAME, TRANSITIONCOMMENT, TITLE, LASTMODIFIEDDATE FROM CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY WHERE (CONTENTSTATUSHISTORYID = (SELECT MAX(CONTENTSTATUSHISTORYID) FROM CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY WHERE (REVISIONID = :"PSXParam/sys_revision" and CONTENTID = :"PSXParam/sys_contentid") ))
